Items database:
  Model [Item]
    id | String
    name | String
    note | String
    created | DateTime
    updated | DateTime
    amount | int
    tags | int[]
    creator | String (userId)
    shared | String[] (userId)
    favorite | boolean
    files | File[]
    location | String ('home', 'basement' ...)
  ☐ Presets as a list of already added data
  ☐ Take foto and scan with ML to add items

Quick timeline [EVENTS]:
  Model [Event]
    id | String
    done | boolean
    name | String
    note | String
    priority | int (0-9)
    created | DateTime
    updated | DateTime
    start | DateTime
    end | DateTime
    tags | int[]
    creator | String (userId)
    shared | String[] (userId)
    favorite | boolean
    recurring | Event[]
    files | File[]
  ☐ Presets
  ☐ Showing all events/todos at one place
  ☐ Filtering by the type of event

